Title: Solve for Leaf Temperature Using Energy Balance
Authors@R: person("Chris", "Muir", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "cdmuir@hawaii.edu", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2555-3878"))
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), units (>= 0.6.0)
